item.title: Welcome
item.description: Hello and welcome to data-handyman.com I’m glad you came to look at my web site! The process of getting this site online has been fun and I’ve been learning some fun stuff. The purpose of this site is to let you know about the ways that a data handyman can help your data related projects. I want you to see how your project can benefit from topics discussed on this site, what has benefited me, and how to do more with less.
